# Testing Rules

## General

- Every bug fix should include a regression test when practical.
- Every business rule should have a test or a manual verification path.
- Do not claim tests passed unless they were actually run.

## Backend Commands

Use commands appropriate to the project:

- `./mvnw test`
- `mvn test`
- `./gradlew test`
- `gradle test`

For Spring Boot API/security/database changes, prefer integration tests if available.

## Mobile Commands

Use:

- `flutter analyze`
- `flutter test`

For networking or Android manifest changes, also verify release/profile configuration.

## Completion Format

Always include:

- Tests run
- Tests not run
- Manual checks needed
- Remaining risks
